<div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
        <div class="event">
            <h3 class="heading"><%= @event.title %> (<%= @event.date.strftime('%-m/%-d/%Y') %>, 7pm) with <%= @event.presenters.collect { |presenter| presenter.name }.join (" and ") %></h3>

            <p><%= @event.description %> You can RSVP <a href="<%= @event.event_link %>">here</a>, if you like!</p>

            <p>In addition to <a href="http://www.pillartechnology.com">Pillar Technology</a>, who sponsors us by giving
                us a place to meet, we are also sponsored by <a href="http://detroitlabs.com/">Detroit Labs</a>, who will
                be buying us food!</p>

            </p>If you want to submit a talk proposal for Craftsman Guild, you can do it
            <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1CCTJ2kjZPrEkCQG6lSqjS7U9MIGd9fELBal1-cbZsMM/viewform">here</a>.</p>

            <% @event.presenters.each { |presenter| %>
                <% unless presenter.bio == nil || presenter.bio.empty? %>
                    <h3 class="heading">About <%= presenter.name %>!</h3>

                    <p><%= presenter.bio %></p>
                <%  end %>
            <% } %>

        </div>

    </div>
</div>

<div class="row-fluid index-footer">
    <div class="about span4">
        <h3 class="heading">About Us!</h3>

        <p>We're a group of programmers who meets up to talk about anything related to programming, usually with an
            emphasis on TDD and clean code! Anything that helps us learn, grow, and teach with regards to software. We
            meet every other Tuesday at 7:00pm at <a href="http://forge.pillartechnology.com">The Forge</a>. We also
            have a <a href="http://groups.google.com/group/craftsman-guild">Google Group</a> if you'd like to join!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="donate span4">
        <h3 class="heading">Sponsors</h3>

        <p>Craftsman Guild is sponsored by <a href="http://detroitlabs.com/">Detroit Labs</a> and
            <a href="http://pillartechnology.com/">Pillar Technology</a>. Without their generous contributions,
            Craftsman Guild wouldn't be cozy experience we all know and love. Thank you, Detroit Labs & Pillar
            Technology!
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="twitter span4">
        <a class="twitter-timeline" href="https://twitter.com/CraftsmanGuild" data-widget-id="304022224862593024">Tweets
            by @CraftsmanGuild</a>
        <script>!function (d, s, id) {
            var js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];
            if (!d.getElementById(id)) {
                js = d.createElement(s);
